Media personality,  Amanda Chisom has been arrested over her alleged participation in a “N50bn” Ponzi scheme carried out by Marksman Chinedu Ijeoma a.k.a Chinmark. Media personality, Chukwudi Iwuchukwu who shared a video of her arriving at the office of FCID in Abuja after she was arrested, said she might be detained for a long time based on a court order procured by the victims of the Chinmark’s heist that she was allegedly part of.